  "title": "CacheStore",
  "description": "Persistent storage backend used by the Loader to cache processed asset data between sessions. Each method accepts a `storageName` namespace (sourced from AssetFactory.storageName) and a per-asset `key`, allowing a single store to hold data for multiple asset types. IndexedDbStore is the built-in implementation backed by the browser's IndexedDB API.",
